Validium is a Layer 2 scaling solution for the Ethereum blockchain. It uses a rollup architecture to aggregate transactions off-chain and then submit the results on-chain. This allows Validium to achieve high throughput and low fees while still maintaining the security of the Ethereum blockchain.

Validium is still under development, but it has the potential to be a major scaling solution for Ethereum. It could help to make Ethereum more scalable and accessible to a wider range of users.

